base32hex

============================================================

base32 from RFC 4648 implemented in the form of a
commandline tool.

Use like so:

$ base32hex encode <stallman_copypasta.txt
$ base32hex decode <base32hex_encoded_file

Algo is from the knot-dns[1] project and so is the LICENSE.

Build with make.

============================================================

[1] https://knot-dns.cz
